# 5P421-220036 - Large Animal Incinerator

## Tender Announcement

The Department of Public Works and Government Services (PSPC) announces a Request for Proposal for the procurement of a Large Animal Incinerator.

### Tender Details

* **Tender Reference Number**: WS3866916337-Doc3876109469
* **Amendment Number**: 1
* **Solicitation Number**: WS3866916337
* **Publication Date**: May 17, 2023
* **Tender Closing Date and Time**: June 8, 2023 at 2:00 PM EDT
* **Expected Contract Start Date**: September 28, 2023
* **Expected Contract End Date**: March 29, 2024
* **Tender Status**: Cancelled

### Solicitation Information

* **Category**: Goods and Services (GD)
* **Procurement Method**: Competitive - Open bidding
* **Selection Criteria**: Lowest Price
* **Trade Agreements**: Goods and Services (GD) Open to all qualified bidders, subject to applicable trade agreements.

### Contracting Entity

* **Department of Public Works and Government Services (PSPC)**
* **11 Laurier St, Phase III, Place du Portage, Gatineau, Quebec, K1A 0S5, Canada**

### End User Entity

* **Parks Canada Agency (PC)**
* **30 Victoria Street, Gatineau, Quebec, J8X 0B3, Canada**

### Contact Information

* **Rachinski, Douglas (SPAC/PSPC)**
* **Douglas.Rachinski@TPSGC-PWGSC.GC.CA**

## Tender Description

Parks Canada Agency requires the supply, delivery, and installation of one (1) Large Animal Incinerator to Banff National Park. The contractor must submit all supporting documentation and bids by June 8, 2023 at 1400 EDT. Any bids submitted after this time will be declared non-responsive.

**Important:** all required supporting documentation and bid submission must be submitted by June 8, 2023 at 1400 EDT.

Please refer to the Ariba Discovery posting and CanadaBuys posting for additional information. The Request for Proposal can be found at the following URL: [http://discovery.ariba.com/rfx/16308901?extsite=MTYzMDg5MDFfQU4wMTQ4NDA
